headline: Wells Fargo (WFC) Beats Q1 Earnings Estimates
summary: Wells Fargo (WFC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 3.25% and 3.12%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
